  m_text: "Chiikawa is gentle, sweet, and kind. Cautious to step out of their comfort
    zone, and somewhat shy, Chiikawa often gets nervous which usually results in
    anxious tears. Thankfully, best friends Hachiware and Usagi always has this cute
    and small creature\u2019s back. "
